nodes.text: Port Epsilon was a spaceport in the city Oluna Biqua, on Genarius.

Port Epsilon was a covered port and was used as Oluna Biqua's emergency port and to bring in hazardous materials or anything else that was unsuitable for the normal landing bays. During the Clone Wars, the Heroes of Cularin traveled to Oluna Biqua aboard the YT-1220 Headliner and it was ordered to land in Port Epsilon. The Cerean Ti-Ori Tamun and twelve members of the Oluna Biqua Elite Guard met them there.
